casebody.data:
Mary ST. GERMAIN, Appellant/Petitioner(s),
v.
U.S. BANK NATIONAL ASSOCIATION, Appellee/Respondent(s). CASE NO.: 2D17-4569 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Second District. February 01, 2018

BY ORDER OF THE COURT:

The appellee's motion to dismiss is granted. This appeal is dismissed as from a nonappealable nonfinal order. See Londono v. Turkey Creek, Inc., 609 So. 2d 14 , 20 (Fla. 1992) ; cf. Floridian Cmty. Bank, Inc. v. Bloom, 25 So. 3d 43 (Fla. 4th DCA 2009).

LaROSE, C.J., and VILLANTI and SALARIO, JJ., Concur.
